    <h1>Accessibility Statement</h1>
    <p>How Roe Valley Residents Association is working to make this website usable, readable, and welcoming for as many people as possible.</p>
    <div class="accessibility-meta">
      <span class="accessibility-pill">Last updated: 1 June 2026</span>
      <span class="accessibility-pill">Website hosted on GitHub Pages</span>
    </div>
